PEOPLE
v.
FORNEY S238013 Supreme Court of California May 10, 2017

*146Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal for the First Appellate District, Division One, for reconsideration in light of the decision in People v. Garcia (2017) 2 Cal.5th 792, 216 Cal.Rptr.3d 75, 391 P.3d 1153.
